Invocation Name: safe trip rio
des:
If you've decided to visit Rio de Janeiro and don't want to ruin your trip, listen to these precious tips from those who have lived in the city of Rio de Janeiro and Copacabana for decades.

* Rio de Janeiro is wonderful, but this skill is not meant to exalt the side, this skill was made to show the real problems that nobody talks about.

We want you to have a peaceful and safe trip to rio de janeiro, listen to these tips carefully and enjoy your vacation.
